						               													<description>Little Red Riding Hood is back, and she wants her revenge against The Big Bad Wolf. How will she get it? Well, she's acquired a couple of supernatural powers, of course! Namely, the ability to create multiples of herself, and make forest trees sprout up suddenly from the ground. Will it be enough to show the wolf she means business? In this 2 player game, you play as either Red or the Wolf, and then switch roles to play again.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Red player draws 3 cards a turn and places them in an expanding grid with new cards touching an old card orthogonally.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Wolf player moves one space a turn orthogonally or diagonally trying to &amp;quot;eat&amp;quot; any &amp;quot;Red&amp;quot; card by entering that card's space.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The match ends when the deck is exhausted or the Wolf is surrounded on all sides and plays a &amp;quot;Red&amp;quot; card on top of the Wolf.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then players switch roles and play another match.  The winner is the wolf who eats the most &amp;quot;Red&amp;quot; cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
